2:T719,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is AIVA better than Soundraw?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. AIVA scores 7.0 overall while Soundraw scores 6.0. AIVA is best for film and game composers and orchestral and classical music, while Soundraw excels for video creators needing background music and royalty-free music production."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, AIVA or Soundraw?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"AIVA starts at $11/mo and Soundraw starts at $16.99/mo. AIVA offers a free plan. Soundraw offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from AIVA to Soundraw?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both AIVA and Soundraw support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about AIVA vs Soundraw?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, AIVA holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Soundraw has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise AIVA for excellent orchestral compositions and Soundraw for fully royalty-free."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, AIVA or Soundraw?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend AIVA for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Soundraw remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize fully royalty-free. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",n