6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both AIVA and Soundraw share a solid foundation of core features including Music Generation. Interestingly, both platforms offer nearly identical feature sets. The difference lies more in the implementation quality and depth of each feature rather than feature availability itself. \n\nLooking at user ratings, AIVA holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Soundraw scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, AIVA offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $11/mo, compared to Soundraw's starting price of $16.99/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. AIVA's free tier and Soundraw's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
